Text.SourceString: I was grinning ear to ear when I woke up this morning...all because of you...
Text.LocalizedString: I was grinning ear to ear when I woke up this morning...all because of you...

Text.SourceString: How'd you like our wedding, babe? I had the time of my life...it's gonna be a day to remember.
Text.LocalizedString: How'd you like our wedding, babe? I had the time of my life...it's gonna be a day to remember.

Text.SourceString: Can't believe you actually let me bring over that neon sign, haha! <NPCName>Rafael</> lost a bet on that one.//<NPCName>Ben</> gave it to me as some sort of joke gift... I'm still trying to figure out the punchline.
Text.LocalizedString: Can't believe you actually let me bring over that neon sign, haha! <NPCName>Rafael</> lost a bet on that one.//<NPCName>Ben</> gave it to me as some sort of joke gift... I'm still trying to figure out the punchline.

Text.SourceString: Good morning, sunshine! How was your sleep?//Get ready for the best breakfast ever. I made this for you! Enjoy.
Text.LocalizedString: Good morning, sunshine! How was your sleep?//Get ready for the best breakfast ever. I made this for you! Enjoy.

Text.SourceString: Babe, I made something super special for you.//My secret ingredient is love...and extra butter.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, I made something super special for you.//My secret ingredient is love...and extra butter.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>... I just wanna say, I love you. You're my favorite person.
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>... I just wanna say, I love you. You're my favorite person.

Text.SourceString: Never forget that, alright?
Text.LocalizedString: Never forget that, alright?

Text.SourceString: You are smokin', baby! Wow, I'm the luckiest husband in the world!
Text.LocalizedString: You are smokin', baby! Wow, I'm the luckiest husband in the world!

Text.SourceString: It's a beautiful day, isn't it? Maybe we can take a walk later.
Text.LocalizedString: It's a beautiful day, isn't it? Maybe we can take a walk later.

Text.SourceString: It's raining outside... How about we snuggle up in bed all day today? Keep each other nice and warm?
Text.LocalizedString: It's raining outside... How about we snuggle up in bed all day today? Keep each other nice and warm?

Text.SourceString: Wanna watch some TV, babe? I can make popcorn.
Text.LocalizedString: Wanna watch some TV, babe? I can make popcorn.

Text.SourceString: Took a stroll this morning, made my way to the lighthouse and back... This place is breathtaking, never gets old.
Text.LocalizedString: Took a stroll this morning, made my way to the lighthouse and back... This place is breathtaking, never gets old.

Text.SourceString: Ready to start the day?
Text.LocalizedString: Ready to start the day?

Text.SourceString: Babe, guess what? I totally rocked the handyman role today. I changed the lightbulbs in our bedroom and did a little inspection around the house.//<portrait=angry>I found some dead ones in the kitchen too. Can you believe it?
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, guess what? I totally rocked the handyman role today. I changed the lightbulbs in our bedroom and did a little inspection around the house.//<portrait=angry>I found some dead ones in the kitchen too. Can you believe it?

Text.SourceString: But no worries, I fixed it all up. It's all good now.
Text.LocalizedString: But no worries, I fixed it all up. It's all good now.

Text.SourceString: I put on some mold treatment in our kitchen. Do you think it's safe to use now?
Text.LocalizedString: I put on some mold treatment in our kitchen. Do you think it's safe to use now?

Text.SourceString: By the way, this week I have a meeting with the mayor. Gotta report for the festival decoration.//<portrait=happy>The pet festival has us putting in the whole town's effort. Better start early...
Text.LocalizedString: By the way, this week I have a meeting with the mayor. Gotta report for the festival decoration.//<portrait=happy>The pet festival has us putting in the whole town's effort. Better start early...

Text.SourceString: Those fake gravestones were ridiculously heavy to carry.//<NpcName>Rafael</> and I made 'em ourselves, and let me tell you, using actual concrete was a bold move...but maybe not the smartest.
Text.LocalizedString: Those fake gravestones were ridiculously heavy to carry.//<NpcName>Rafael</> and I made 'em ourselves, and let me tell you, using actual concrete was a bold move...but maybe not the smartest.

Text.SourceString: I'm looking forward to the ogoh-ogoh parade. That's definitely the highlight of the Spooky Festival, hands down!//<portrait=normal>I heard from <NpcName>Alice</> that it's supposed to ward off the evil spirits. Pretty cool, right?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm looking forward to the ogoh-ogoh parade. That's definitely the highlight of the Spooky Festival, hands down!//<portrait=normal>I heard from <NpcName>Alice</> that it's supposed to ward off the evil spirits. Pretty cool, right?

Text.SourceString: The change of seasons here in Coral Island happens in the blink of an eye. Feels like it just sneaks up on ya overnight, you know? But hey, I'm diggin' it.
Text.LocalizedString: The change of seasons here in Coral Island happens in the blink of an eye. Feels like it just sneaks up on ya overnight, you know? But hey, I'm diggin' it.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should borrow one of <NpcName>Rafael</>'s beanies. It could keep my ears warm, but I don't know...//<portrait=concerned>It might mess up my hair.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should borrow one of <NpcName>Rafael</>'s beanies. It could keep my ears warm, but I don't know...//<portrait=concerned>It might mess up my hair.

Text.SourceString: Babe, I had to put my puffer jacket in your drawer. It wouldn't fit in mine. Hope that's cool with you.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, I had to put my puffer jacket in your drawer. It wouldn't fit in mine. Hope that's cool with you.

Text.SourceString: Hmm... I feel like I need to shave... What do you think, <PlayerName>$Player</>?//Should I go for a clean-cut look or wait another week?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm... I feel like I need to shave... What do you think, <PlayerName>$Player</>?//Should I go for a clean-cut look or wait another week?

Text.SourceString: Check it out, I can kinda see the lighthouse from here... see that top bit over there?
Text.LocalizedString: Check it out, I can kinda see the lighthouse from here... see that top bit over there?

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking we should treat ourselves to some pizza for dinner. After that intense workout today, I definitely <Italic>need</> some pizza...
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking we should treat ourselves to some pizza for dinner. After that intense workout today, I definitely <Italic>need</> some pizza...

Text.SourceString: Get over here, you...give me a kiss.//I miss you, <PlayerName>$Player</>...
Text.LocalizedString: Get over here, you...give me a kiss.//I miss you, <PlayerName>$Player</>...

Text.SourceString: You worked so hard on our farm today, babe. You deserve some rest.//Let me take care of you. How about a massage later?
Text.LocalizedString: You worked so hard on our farm today, babe. You deserve some rest.//Let me take care of you. How about a massage later?

Text.SourceString: So, how's my farmer doing today?
Text.LocalizedString: So, how's my farmer doing today?

Text.SourceString: Should we call it a night soon?
Text.LocalizedString: Should we call it a night soon?

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking maybe I'll take <NpcName>Rafael</> out tonight, you know, get him out of the house.//<portrait=concerned>I feel bad seeing him cooped up inside all the time.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking maybe I'll take <NpcName>Rafael</> out tonight, you know, get him out of the house.//<portrait=concerned>I feel bad seeing him cooped up inside all the time.

Text.SourceString: Hey, babe, thanks for checking up on <NpcName>Rafael</> every now and then.//He rarely gets visitors, so I appreciate it.
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, babe, thanks for checking up on <NpcName>Rafael</> every now and then.//He rarely gets visitors, so I appreciate it.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Raj</> makes some killer coffee, no doubt about it.//<portrait=surprised>But you won't believe it, they turned down my idea of selling pumpkin pies. Can you believe that?
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Raj</> makes some killer coffee, no doubt about it.//<portrait=surprised>But you won't believe it, they turned down my idea of selling pumpkin pies. Can you believe that?

Text.SourceString: What do you think about commissioning <NpcName>Dinda</> to build us an extra shed for some epic pool nights?//But then we'd have to find someone to make a pool table... I don't think they offer that service.
Text.LocalizedString: What do you think about commissioning <NpcName>Dinda</> to build us an extra shed for some epic pool nights?//But then we'd have to find someone to make a pool table... I don't think they offer that service.

Text.SourceString: Babe, you won't believe it. <NPCName>Luke</> just showed me his new speakers, and whoa!//<portrait=normal>The sound quality is out of this world. It's like being right there at a live concert. Super cool!
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, you won't believe it. <NPCName>Luke</> just showed me his new speakers, and whoa!//<portrait=normal>The sound quality is out of this world. It's like being right there at a live concert. Super cool!

Text.SourceString: I can hear <NPCName>Jack</>'s cattle from here. It's so relaxing.
Text.LocalizedString: I can hear <NPCName>Jack</>'s cattle from here. It's so relaxing.

Text.SourceString: This is my favorite spot.
Text.LocalizedString: This is my favorite spot.

Text.SourceString: I saw some lizards outside our window this morning. No worries, though—I made sure to keep the window shut tight. Can't have them sneaking in, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: I saw some lizards outside our window this morning. No worries, though—I made sure to keep the window shut tight. Can't have them sneaking in, huh?

Text.SourceString: It's snowing out, babe. I'll take care of scraping the snow off our window later, okay?//Maybe after lunch.
Text.LocalizedString: It's snowing out, babe. I'll take care of scraping the snow off our window later, okay?//Maybe after lunch.

Text.SourceString: Oh, and I already cleared the pathways in front of our door for you.//It should be all good now.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, and I already cleared the pathways in front of our door for you.//It should be all good now.

Text.SourceString: I'm really hoping <NPCName>Rafael</> joins us for the New Year's Eve party tomorrow. It's not cool for him to be alone on such a new year.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm really hoping <NPCName>Rafael</> joins us for the New Year's Eve party tomorrow. It's not cool for him to be alone on such a new year.

Text.SourceString: Well, I guess it's alright, but you know, I'd prefer him to have some company.//<portrait=sad>I'll have a chat with him later, see how he's doing.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, I guess it's alright, but you know, I'd prefer him to have some company.//<portrait=sad>I'll have a chat with him later, see how he's doing.

Text.SourceString: The mayor asked me to check on the boat for the festival tomorrow. Everything's in top condition and ready to go.
Text.LocalizedString: The mayor asked me to check on the boat for the festival tomorrow. Everything's in top condition and ready to go.

Text.SourceString: I'm super excited about getting those giant balloons out for the Beach Cleanup. It's gonna be epic.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm super excited about getting those giant balloons out for the Beach Cleanup. It's gonna be epic.

Text.SourceString: When Alun-Alun turns all pink during the Cherry Blossom Festival...ah, it's so stunning, just like you.
Text.LocalizedString: When Alun-Alun turns all pink during the Cherry Blossom Festival...ah, it's so stunning, just like you.

Text.SourceString: It’s important to have a hobby.//Gives you a chance to really dig deep into who you are.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s important to have a hobby.//Gives you a chance to really dig deep into who you are.

Text.SourceString: It's the small stuff, like how we entertain ourselves…//They’re what makes us who we are, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: It's the small stuff, like how we entertain ourselves…//They’re what makes us who we are, eh?

Text.SourceString: Did you know <NPCName>Frank</> hates yogurt?//<portrait=normal>A weird thing to hate, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: Did you know <NPCName>Frank</> hates yogurt?//<portrait=normal>A weird thing to hate, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: He also hates durian, but that, I get.//<portrait=concerned>I wouldn't touch a durian with a ten-metre pole.
Text.LocalizedString: He also hates durian, but that, I get.//<portrait=concerned>I wouldn't touch a durian with a ten-metre pole.

Text.SourceString: When it comes to birthdays, people mostly just appreciate you remembering. Kinda shows they're in your thoughts.
Text.LocalizedString: When it comes to birthdays, people mostly just appreciate you remembering. Kinda shows they're in your thoughts.

Text.SourceString: But hey, gifts never hurt either!
Text.LocalizedString: But hey, gifts never hurt either!

Text.SourceString: Your tools holding up all right, baby?
Text.LocalizedString: Your tools holding up all right, baby?

Text.SourceString: Bring 'em to the shop if they need some work, okay? I'll take care of it.
Text.LocalizedString: Bring 'em to the shop if they need some work, okay? I'll take care of it.

Text.SourceString: It’s <Italic>finally</> getting warmer. Can't wait to get back outside.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s <Italic>finally</> getting warmer. Can't wait to get back outside.

Text.SourceString: The Cherry Blossom Festival was out of this world.//<portrait=happy>Good people, great food, what's better than that?
Text.LocalizedString: The Cherry Blossom Festival was out of this world.//<portrait=happy>Good people, great food, what's better than that?

Text.SourceString: Workshop's not too hot right now. Kinda nice and warm, really.
Text.LocalizedString: Workshop's not too hot right now. Kinda nice and warm, really.

Text.SourceString: Spring always brings so much life. Kinda makes me feel more alive too.
Text.LocalizedString: Spring always brings so much life. Kinda makes me feel more alive too.

Text.SourceString: <Italic>Gah</>, I love Summer! Everyone's out and about, having a good time.//<portrait=blushing>And I gotta say, I think I look pretty good in Summer clothes. What do you think?
Text.LocalizedString: <Italic>Gah</>, I love Summer! Everyone's out and about, having a good time.//<portrait=blushing>And I gotta say, I think I look pretty good in Summer clothes. What do you think?

Text.SourceString: I was reminded yesterday how I hate working in front of the furnace in Summer. I bet you never felt heat like the heat of a furnace on a hot Summer day.
Text.LocalizedString: I was reminded yesterday how I hate working in front of the furnace in Summer. I bet you never felt heat like the heat of a furnace on a hot Summer day.

Text.SourceString: How can I work inside on such a beautiful day?//<portrait=sad>Sometimes being a blacksmith sucks.
Text.LocalizedString: How can I work inside on such a beautiful day?//<portrait=sad>Sometimes being a blacksmith sucks.

Text.SourceString: I'm not even exaggerating when I say the Beach Cleanup Festival is my favorite. Love seeing the community come together like that.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not even exaggerating when I say the Beach Cleanup Festival is my favorite. Love seeing the community come together like that.

Text.SourceString: The trash collecting isn’t a contest per se, but…//<portrait=blushing>I like to think it is.
Text.LocalizedString: The trash collecting isn’t a contest per se, but…//<portrait=blushing>I like to think it is.

Text.SourceString: Can't figure out why my little bro keeps staying inside. Doesn't he get that Summer is the best time to be out and about?
Text.LocalizedString: Can't figure out why my little bro keeps staying inside. Doesn't he get that Summer is the best time to be out and about?

Text.SourceString: So glad it's starting to cool down. Makes working at the shop a lot easier.
Text.LocalizedString: So glad it's starting to cool down. Makes working at the shop a lot easier.

Text.SourceString: I can't wait for the Harvest Festival. What are we gonna show, babe?!
Text.LocalizedString: I can't wait for the Harvest Festival. What are we gonna show, babe?!

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking about heading over to the hot spring one of these days… Clear out some leaves for <NPCName>Takeba</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking about heading over to the hot spring one of these days… Clear out some leaves for <NPCName>Takeba</>.

Text.SourceString: It’s starting to get too cold for my taste. I’m not looking forward to Winter…//<portrait=blushing>A hot spring does sound pretty sweet right about now. What do you say we hit the hot spring next week? Together...when nobody's around...the whole place for ourselves.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s starting to get too cold for my taste. I’m not looking forward to Winter…//<portrait=blushing>A hot spring does sound pretty sweet right about now. What do you say we hit the hot spring next week? Together...when nobody's around...the whole place for ourselves.

Text.SourceString: Winter is such a bummer.//I can’t stand being outdoors in the cold too long.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter is such a bummer.//I can’t stand being outdoors in the cold too long.

Text.SourceString: You know what? Sometimes Winter isn’t so bad. At the very least, it makes working in front of the furnace so much better.//<portrait=sad>I’d still rather be outside, though…
Text.LocalizedString: You know what? Sometimes Winter isn’t so bad. At the very least, it makes working in front of the furnace so much better.//<portrait=sad>I’d still rather be outside, though…

Text.SourceString: On one hand, I get so bored cooped up inside. On the other hand, it’s so dang cold out!//<portrait=sad>What should I do?
Text.LocalizedString: On one hand, I get so bored cooped up inside. On the other hand, it’s so dang cold out!//<portrait=sad>What should I do?

Text.SourceString: My little brother and I used to play in the snow until late. When we were kids, of course.//We’d make sleighs from tree trunks and just go sliding back and forth.
Text.LocalizedString: My little brother and I used to play in the snow until late. When we were kids, of course.//We’d make sleighs from tree trunks and just go sliding back and forth.

Text.SourceString: It doesn’t really feel like Winter until I see the festive Winter decorations.
Text.LocalizedString: It doesn’t really feel like Winter until I see the festive Winter decorations.

Text.SourceString: I'm pretty much over Winter. Can't wait for Spring to roll in.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm pretty much over Winter. Can't wait for Spring to roll in.

Text.SourceString: School’s important. I’m glad we get to keep the school going on such a small island.
Text.LocalizedString: School’s important. I’m glad we get to keep the school going on such a small island.

Text.SourceString: Had a chat with <NpcName>Randy</> about it, and keeping the education budget afloat is no picnic.
Text.LocalizedString: Had a chat with <NpcName>Randy</> about it, and keeping the education budget afloat is no picnic.

Text.SourceString: Ugh, today’s a busy day for me. I could use a cold drink right about now.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, today’s a busy day for me. I could use a cold drink right about now.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I went over to the inn and had a quick dinner with our niece, <NPCName>Valentina</>, to celebrate her birthday last week.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I went over to the inn and had a quick dinner with our niece, <NPCName>Valentina</>, to celebrate her birthday last week.

Text.SourceString: I gave her a geode... Thought she'd get a kick out of a geode, hunting for treasures and all, but I guess I missed the mark…
Text.LocalizedString: I gave her a geode... Thought she'd get a kick out of a geode, hunting for treasures and all, but I guess I missed the mark…

Text.SourceString: The annual beach cleanup's taking place near the inn, and I'm sure everyone's gonna chip in.
Text.LocalizedString: The annual beach cleanup's taking place near the inn, and I'm sure everyone's gonna chip in.

Text.SourceString: Any reason is a good reason to get together, eh, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Any reason is a good reason to get together, eh, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: Fall is here, and I haven’t gotten anything for <NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday yet…
Text.LocalizedString: Fall is here, and I haven’t gotten anything for <NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday yet…

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> loves onyx. I sure hope <NPCName>Ben</> has some in stock right now...
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> loves onyx. I sure hope <NPCName>Ben</> has some in stock right now...

Text.SourceString: For<NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday last week, I gave him some cake from the Tavern. He seemed to like it.
Text.LocalizedString: For<NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday last week, I gave him some cake from the Tavern. He seemed to like it.

Text.SourceString: Next Summer, I’m going to remind myself to set aside one piece of onyx for his birthday. Because I know <NPCName>Rafael</> loves that stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: Next Summer, I’m going to remind myself to set aside one piece of onyx for his birthday. Because I know <NPCName>Rafael</> loves that stuff.

Text.SourceString: I’m cold. Why does it have to be this cold?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m cold. Why does it have to be this cold?

Text.SourceString: *shivers*
Text.LocalizedString: *shivers*

Text.SourceString: It can get pretty boring being indoors all day.
Text.LocalizedString: It can get pretty boring being indoors all day.

Text.SourceString: With this cold, there's hardly anyone out and about.
Text.LocalizedString: With this cold, there's hardly anyone out and about.

Text.SourceString: I try to catch up with my niece and cousins when I can.//<NPCName>Rafael</> and I have this ongoing bet about who's the better uncle to <NPCName>Valentina</>.//<portrait=blushing>Who do you think is ahead?
Text.LocalizedString: I try to catch up with my niece and cousins when I can.//<NPCName>Rafael</> and I have this ongoing bet about who's the better uncle to <NPCName>Valentina</>.//<portrait=blushing>Who do you think is ahead?

Text.SourceString: Anyway, those girls are always up to something.///<portrait=happy>Ha ha! I’d hate to miss any of it.
Text.LocalizedString: Anyway, those girls are always up to something.///<portrait=happy>Ha ha! I’d hate to miss any of it.

Text.SourceString: Does it feel like it rains more in Summer, or is it just me?
Text.LocalizedString: Does it feel like it rains more in Summer, or is it just me?

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I used to play in the mud in weather like this.//<portrait=happy>We’d get in so much trouble when Mom found out.//Ha! Good times.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I used to play in the mud in weather like this.//<portrait=happy>We’d get in so much trouble when Mom found out.//Ha! Good times.

Text.SourceString: I might go to the Tavern after work and play some pool.//<portrait=happy>Does that sound okay to you, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: I might go to the Tavern after work and play some pool.//<portrait=happy>Does that sound okay to you, babe?

Text.SourceString: You're welcome to join!
Text.LocalizedString: You're welcome to join!

Text.SourceString: It’s storming really hard outside, so I might as well keep the furnace on and get some work done.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s storming really hard outside, so I might as well keep the furnace on and get some work done.

Text.SourceString: Are you here because you miss me or here on business, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you here because you miss me or here on business, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: I can’t believe it’s still storming.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t believe it’s still storming.

Text.SourceString: Well, I guess it is Winter.//<portrait=concerned>What else did I expect, besides getting snowed on?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, I guess it is Winter.//<portrait=concerned>What else did I expect, besides getting snowed on?

Text.SourceString: Ouch! Watch your step!
Text.LocalizedString: Ouch! Watch your step!

Text.SourceString: No worries…//<portrait=normal>With it being this cold, my toes are probably numb anyways.
Text.LocalizedString: No worries…//<portrait=normal>With it being this cold, my toes are probably numb anyways.

Text.SourceString: Baby, you’re covered in snow!
Text.LocalizedString: Baby, you’re covered in snow!

Text.SourceString: You should probably stay put for a bit, warm up some.
Text.LocalizedString: You should probably stay put for a bit, warm up some.

Text.SourceString: Long day today, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Long day today, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: My arms are tired from working all day, but never too tired for a good game of pool!
Text.LocalizedString: My arms are tired from working all day, but never too tired for a good game of pool!

Text.SourceString: My left eye feels funny.//<portrait=annoyed>I think I got dust in it on my way here…
Text.LocalizedString: My left eye feels funny.//<portrait=annoyed>I think I got dust in it on my way here…

Text.SourceString: Why is it always in my left eye?//<portrait=happy>I guess it’s time for a new eye. Ha!//<portrait=sad>Thank you, babe, for putting up with my dad joke this long. Haha.
Text.LocalizedString: Why is it always in my left eye?//<portrait=happy>I guess it’s time for a new eye. Ha!//<portrait=sad>Thank you, babe, for putting up with my dad joke this long. Haha.

Text.SourceString: Can I stay for one more round of pool? Please?//YES!!!
Text.LocalizedString: Can I stay for one more round of pool? Please?//YES!!!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</>'s a real whiz. He knows more about crafting quality weapons than I do.//He's got skills.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</>'s a real whiz. He knows more about crafting quality weapons than I do.//He's got skills.

Text.SourceString: He's usually the one handling the final fold of the weapon too.
Text.LocalizedString: He's usually the one handling the final fold of the weapon too.

Text.SourceString: This spot sure gets a lot of foot traffic, huh?//<portrait=annoyed>I always see <NPCName>Anne</> and <NPCName>Paul</> walking around here.
Text.LocalizedString: This spot sure gets a lot of foot traffic, huh?//<portrait=annoyed>I always see <NPCName>Anne</> and <NPCName>Paul</> walking around here.

Text.SourceString: It’s true. Their house is right over there.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s true. Their house is right over there.

Text.SourceString: I’m just getting out for some fresh air…and some ore.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m just getting out for some fresh air…and some ore.

Text.SourceString: It’s probably not the healthiest habit, staying indoors all day.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s probably not the healthiest habit, staying indoors all day.

Text.SourceString: [<NPCName>Pablo</> is hard at work on his speaker.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NPCName>Pablo</> is hard at work on his speaker.]

Text.SourceString: Smell that?//Sweet Spring air! I’m so glad Winter is over. Ha ha.
Text.LocalizedString: Smell that?//Sweet Spring air! I’m so glad Winter is over. Ha ha.

Text.SourceString: The temperature outside only feels right to me in Summer.//Maybe because I’m always in front of a furnace?
Text.LocalizedString: The temperature outside only feels right to me in Summer.//Maybe because I’m always in front of a furnace?

Text.SourceString: Read anything interesting lately, <PlayerName>$player</>?//Tell me all about it… I like hearing you talk about the books you read.
Text.LocalizedString: Read anything interesting lately, <PlayerName>$player</>?//Tell me all about it… I like hearing you talk about the books you read.

Text.SourceString: Seems like every time I turn around, you're out there, lending a hand to someone.//You're one of the good ones.
Text.LocalizedString: Seems like every time I turn around, you're out there, lending a hand to someone.//You're one of the good ones.

Text.SourceString: Hmm… I should read more books.
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm… I should read more books.

Text.SourceString: It’s just so hard to find the time, yeah? Maybe we can read together! And meet up to talk about what we’re reading.//<portrait=normal>Like a book club, but just you and me.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s just so hard to find the time, yeah? Maybe we can read together! And meet up to talk about what we’re reading.//<portrait=normal>Like a book club, but just you and me.

Text.SourceString: I think about my parents a lot.//They made a life for me and <NPCName>Rafael</>. Came here with nothing and made something of themselves. I feel like I owe them something.
Text.LocalizedString: I think about my parents a lot.//They made a life for me and <NPCName>Rafael</>. Came here with nothing and made something of themselves. I feel like I owe them something.

Text.SourceString: I hope they’re happy.
Text.LocalizedString: I hope they’re happy.

Text.SourceString: I don’t mind hard work, to be honest.//I actually kind of like it.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t mind hard work, to be honest.//I actually kind of like it.

Text.SourceString: I couldn’t work a desk job, I don’t think.//I feel like I always have to keep moving my body to keep my mind at ease.
Text.LocalizedString: I couldn’t work a desk job, I don’t think.//I feel like I always have to keep moving my body to keep my mind at ease.

Text.SourceString: If I weren’t a blacksmith, I could certainly see myself as a farmer, to be honest.//<portrait=blushing>I spent a lot of time gardening growing up. Dirt suits me.
Text.LocalizedString: If I weren’t a blacksmith, I could certainly see myself as a farmer, to be honest.//<portrait=blushing>I spent a lot of time gardening growing up. Dirt suits me.

Text.SourceString: Wow! You look fantastic.//Where did you get that outfit?
Text.LocalizedString: Wow! You look fantastic.//Where did you get that outfit?

Text.SourceString: Ugh, I haven’t taken a proper break all week. Been working nonstop.//It’s a busy Winter for me.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, I haven’t taken a proper break all week. Been working nonstop.//It’s a busy Winter for me.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Luke</> and I tinker with our speakers a lot. Well, speakers, TVs, whatever’s in front of us.//<portrait=happy>Not scooters, though. Can’t do that. We don’t know <Italic>jack</> about scooters. That’s more <NPCName>Frank’s</> thing.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Luke</> and I tinker with our speakers a lot. Well, speakers, TVs, whatever’s in front of us.//<portrait=happy>Not scooters, though. Can’t do that. We don’t know <Italic>jack</> about scooters. That’s more <NPCName>Frank’s</> thing.

Text.SourceString: Does it feel stuffy in here to you?//<portrait=angry><NpcName>Rafael</> had to keep the windows shut all Winter, and now it sort of smells like…uh…soup?//What's up with that?
Text.LocalizedString: Does it feel stuffy in here to you?//<portrait=angry><NpcName>Rafael</> had to keep the windows shut all Winter, and now it sort of smells like…uh…soup?//What's up with that?

Text.SourceString: My brother's been talking about starting a garden, like <NpcName>Dippa</>'s.//<portrait=concerned>I don’t know...sounds like a lot. Balancing farming and blacksmithing...//I prefer him to stick to one thing and do it well.
Text.LocalizedString: My brother's been talking about starting a garden, like <NpcName>Dippa</>'s.//<portrait=concerned>I don’t know...sounds like a lot. Balancing farming and blacksmithing...//I prefer him to stick to one thing and do it well.

Text.SourceString: I hate to turn him down, but I think he's just got cabin fever from the Winter.//Now that it's Spring, he's all about getting outdoors, doing springtime things like gardening, cleaning up the cemetery, that sort of thing.
Text.LocalizedString: I hate to turn him down, but I think he's just got cabin fever from the Winter.//Now that it's Spring, he's all about getting outdoors, doing springtime things like gardening, cleaning up the cemetery, that sort of thing.

Text.SourceString: Whoa! Summer looks good on you. Gimme some of that glow!
Text.LocalizedString: Whoa! Summer looks good on you. Gimme some of that glow!

Text.SourceString: It’s too hot to wear anything else right now.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s too hot to wear anything else right now.

Text.SourceString: This necklace is from <NpcName>Valentina</>. She made it from shells she got at the beach.//Creative kid, isn’t she?
Text.LocalizedString: This necklace is from <NpcName>Valentina</>. She made it from shells she got at the beach.//Creative kid, isn’t she?

Text.SourceString: These boots are my favorite. Wear 'em all year round.//They’re good for walking in the snow. They have those teeth that grip your feet to the ground. Anti-slip!
Text.LocalizedString: These boots are my favorite. Wear 'em all year round.//They’re good for walking in the snow. They have those teeth that grip your feet to the ground. Anti-slip!
